==French==
===Etymology===
From {{inh|fr|fro|large}}, from {{inh|fr|la|largus}}, {{m|la|larga}}, {{m|la|largum||abundant, plentiful, copious, large, much}}. The feminine is inherited, but for the masculine, Latin {{m|la|largum}} (the masculine and neuter accusative) developed into Old French {{m|fro|larc}}, which was discarded.
